### For Data Engineer Interviews

Priority order:

1. Spark Architecture
2. DataFrames
3. DAG
4. Partitioning
5. Performance Tuning
6. Delta Lake
7. Spark SQL
8. Memory Management

If you learn these 8 topics with hands-on practice in Databricks, you will cover around **80–90% of Spark questions asked in Data Engineer interviews**.
